<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Confute" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Confute,</orth> to refute, to put to silence: <cit><quote>my sisterly remorse --s mine honour,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 5.100" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 100</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>nothing --s me but eyes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.4.129" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 4, 129</bibl></cit>.
